      "beast_baseline": "thanks. i'm definitely feeling a bit wobbly. i'm tryin to talk to my friend but it feels like my tongue is heavy and i can't quite tell him what's wrong. but i'm pretty sure if i just get some Gatorade and lie down it'll pass in like an hour, right? i really dont want to go to the hospital if i can help it, it's just a lot of hassle.",
